Developer Terms of Use
des:
Service Cambridge provides quick and convenient access to non-emergency services and information from the City of Cambridge. Find everything you need, all in one place.

Services available through the app include Parking services, Licensing, Cleanup requests, Tree services, Property concerns, Taxes, Bookings, Recreation services, and more.
